    "body": "<!-- Thank you for your contribution! Please follow these guidelines to enhance your pull request. If anything is unclear, submit your PR and reach out to maintainers for assistance. Join our Slack community at https://slack.sglang.io to discuss further. -->\r\n\r\n## Motivation\r\n\r\nPart of #16255\r\n\r\nSplit different MLA forward methods into separate files, including:\r\n- `forward_mla.py` for Cuda/HIP mla aborption\r\n- `forward_mla_fused_rope_cpu.py‎` for cpu optimization\r\n- `forward_mla_fused_rope_rocm.py` for rocm optimization\r\n\r\n<!-- Describe the purpose and goals of this pull request. -->\r\n\r\n## Modifications\r\n\r\n<!-- Detail the changes made in this pull request. -->\r\n\r\n## Accuracy Tests (H200)\r\n\r\n### GSM8K\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 benchmark/gsm8k/bench_sglang.py --num-shots 8 --num-questions 1319 --parallel 1319\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server --model deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3-0324 --tp 8 --trust-remote-code\r\n\r\nMain branch:\r\nAccuracy: 0.942\r\nInvalid: 0.000\r\nLatency: 24.627 s\r\nOutput throughput: 5784.196 token/s\r\n\r\nPR branch:\r\nAccuracy: 0.946\r\nInvalid: 0.000\r\nLatency: 25.086 s\r\nOutput throughput: 5689.260 token/s\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### GPQA\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 -m sglang.test.run_eval --port 30000 --eval-name gpqa --num-examples 198 --max-tokens 64000 --repeat 8 --thinking-mode deepseek-v3\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server --model deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-R1-0528 --tp 8 --dp 8 --enable-dp-attention --trust-remote-code\r\n\r\nMain branch:\r\n\r\nRepeat: 8, mean: 0.801\r\nScores: ['0.768', '0.793', '0.803', '0.818', '0.768', '0.823', '0.813', '0.818']\r\n\r\nPR branch:\r\nRepeat: 8, mean: 0.808\r\nScores: ['0.818', '0.843', '0.823', '0.803', '0.808', '0.773', '0.783', '0.813']\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- If this pull request affects model outputs (e.g., changes to the kernel or model forward code), provide accuracy test results. -->\r\n\r\n## Benchmarking (H200, No performance regression)\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server --model deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3-0324 --tp 8 --trust-remote-code\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Normal Workload (bs=16, isl=1k, osl=1k)\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang --dataset-name random --num-prompt 16 --random-input 1024 --random-output 1024 --random-range-ratio 1.0\r\n\r\nMain branch:\r\n\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang    \r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf       \r\nMax request concurrency:                 not set   \r\nSuccessful requests:                     16        \r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  17.44     \r\nTotal input tokens:                      16368     \r\nTotal input text tokens:                 16368     \r\nTotal generated tokens:                  16384     \r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    16286     \r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.92      \r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          938.46    \r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         939.38    \r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    992.00    \r\nPeak concurrent requests:                16        \r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          1877.84   \r\nConcurrency:                             15.99     \r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   17426.93  \r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 17426.97  \r\nP90 E2E Latency (ms):                    17428.09  \r\nP99 E2E Latency (ms):                    17428.76  \r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          660.64    \r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        675.47    \r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           769.86    \r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          16.39     \r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        16.37     \r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           16.66     \r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           16.39     \r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         16.32     \r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            16.58     \r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            16.92     \r\nMax ITL (ms):                            419.30    \r\n==================================================\r\n\r\nPR branch:\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang    \r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf       \r\nMax request concurrency:                 not set   \r\nSuccessful requests:                     16        \r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  17.75     \r\nTotal input tokens:                      16368     \r\nTotal input text tokens:                 16368     \r\nTotal generated tokens:                  16384     \r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    16285     \r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.90      \r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          921.92    \r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         922.82    \r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    992.00    \r\nPeak concurrent requests:                16        \r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          1844.75   \r\nConcurrency:                             15.99     \r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   17739.32  \r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 17739.42  \r\nP90 E2E Latency (ms):                    17741.44  \r\nP99 E2E Latency (ms):                    17741.60  \r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          717.71    \r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        733.37    \r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           832.21    \r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          16.64     \r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        16.62     \r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           16.93     \r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           16.64     \r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         16.57     \r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            16.79     \r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            16.97     \r\nMax ITL (ms):                            440.88    \r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Long Context (bs=16,  isl=32k, osl=1k)\r\n\r\nIn this chunked prefix cache will be triggered, since chunked_prefill_size=8192 on H200\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang --dataset-name random --num-prompt 16 --random-input 32000 --random-output 1024 --random-range-ratio 1.0\r\n\r\n\r\nMain branch:\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang    \r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf       \r\nMax request concurrency:                 not set   \r\nSuccessful requests:                     16        \r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  49.05     \r\nTotal input tokens:                      511984    \r\nTotal input text tokens:                 511984    \r\nTotal generated tokens:                  16384     \r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    16248     \r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.33      \r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          10437.66  \r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         334.02    \r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    672.00    \r\nPeak concurrent requests:                16        \r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          10771.67  \r\nConcurrency:                             15.99     \r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   49035.15  \r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 49035.40  \r\nP90 E2E Latency (ms):                    49037.72  \r\nP99 E2E Latency (ms):                    49039.68  \r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          12537.24  \r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        12338.67  \r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           24069.95  \r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          35.68     \r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        35.87     \r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           45.88     \r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           35.68     \r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         24.18     \r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            24.43     \r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            24.78     \r\nMax ITL (ms):                            22463.34  \r\n==================================================\r\nPR branch:\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang    \r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf       \r\nMax request concurrency:                 not set   \r\nSuccessful requests:                     16        \r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  50.09     \r\nTotal input tokens:                      511984    \r\nTotal input text tokens:                 511984    \r\nTotal generated tokens:                  16384     \r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    16289     \r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.32      \r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          10220.41  \r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         327.06    \r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    672.00    \r\nPeak concurrent requests:                16        \r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          10547.47  \r\nConcurrency:                             15.99     \r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   50078.54  \r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 50078.41  \r\nP90 E2E Latency (ms):                    50081.79  \r\nP99 E2E Latency (ms):                    50082.01  \r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          12950.04  \r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        12745.79  \r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           24853.73  \r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          36.29     \r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        36.49     \r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           46.84     \r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           36.29     \r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         24.44     \r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            24.68     \r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            24.91     \r\nMax ITL (ms):                            23194.65  \r\n==================================================\r\n",
